quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  5,27,"Ne basoomele amakhuwa aka Abaana ba Adam khubwatoto. Olwa bahinia eshihanwa nishifuchililwa shia mulala wabu, ne shiowundi nishilafuchililwa tawe. Yaboola mbu; “Nditsa okhwira” Namukalusia mbu “Nyasaye afuchililanga abamuritsanga”"
  5,28,"“Niwitsa okhundakhwo omukhonokwo mbu unzira, esie shindalakhurakhwo omukhono kwanje okhukhwira tawe, esie eritsanga Nyasaye, Omulesi webindu biosi"
  5,29,"Esie ndenya ochinge tsimbi tsianje nende tsimbi tsitsio, ne khulwa ako obe mubandu bomumulilo. Ne oko niko omurungo kwa Abandu abamabii"
  5,30,"Mana omwoyo kukwe nikumuyila okhwira omusiani wabu, mana namwira, mana naba mubandu bokhusikha"
  5,31,"Awo Nyasaye narera likhokho, nilichaka okhukwota mwiloba kholimwechesie shinga ayabila omulambo kwomusiani wabu. Naboola mbu “abayie! Akhayilwe okhuba shinga likhokho lino, ndafunikha(ndayabila) omulambo kwomwana wafu” mana naba mubandu bokhwiyitsulisia"
  5,32,"Eshichila ako, nikhuhandichila Abana ba Israil mbu, “ulia ulera Omundu- eshikhaya Omundu oyo nalerere Omundu tawe-, nohomba okhukhola obutobela khushialo, alaba shinga wirire Abandu boosi, ne ulia wonokosia Omundu alishinga uwonokosiye Abandu boosi. Ne toto Abarumwa befu babeetsela nende ebifune bili habulafu. Mana abanji mubo imbeli wakano nibaba abeyisasia"
  5,33,"Kho omurungo kwa balia bakhupananga nende Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende okhukhola obubii khushialo, ni okhwirwa nohomba okhubambwa nohomba okhutetwa emikhono chiabu nende ebilenje buchikha, nohomba balondwe mushialo esho. Esho ni eshinyasio shiabu khushialo ne mwikulu balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo"
  5,34,Halali balia betsa okhusaba eshileshelo nimushili okhubatila. Ne manye mbu Nyasaye ni Omunji wobulesheli nende Omunji wetsimbabaasi